It was built in 2015 and features approximately 7,190 square feet of living space with 5 bedrooms, 8 bathrooms, foyer with staircase, formal living & dining rooms, kitchen, breakfast room, family room, office, game room with wet bar, home theater, wine cellar and room, 5-car garage with gated entrance and more.

Outdoor features include a covered patio with kitchen/BBQ, putting green and a resort-style pool with spa, slide, fire pit and 2 bridges.

It was last listed at $2,499,000 (currently off the market)

Goodnight! 😍 This stunning English Tudor style stone home is located on Palm Royale Boulevard in Sugar Land, Texas. 

It was designed by Patrick Berrios Designs and built in 2017 by Sims Luxury Builders. It features over 11,000 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 6 full and 3 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, 2-story great room & dining room, gourmet kitchen with double islands, breakfast room, 2-story family room, home theater and more. 

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, fountain, porte-cochere, covered/uncovered patios, fireplace, kitchen/BBQ and a swimming pool with spa.

Photography by JONATHAN CALVERT 

(Not For Sale)

Good morning! 😍 This Mediterranean style home is located at 5501 Twin Cities Lane in McKinney, Texas and is situated on an acre of land overlooking the TPC Craig Ranch Golf Course.

It was built in 2009 and features approximately 11,219 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 7 full and 2 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, elevator, 2-story great room, formal dining room, wine cellar, gourmet kitchen, golf simulator room, home theater, 8-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a porte-cochere, covered balcony, covered/uncovered patios, BBQ, fireplace, fire pit, giant chess set, spa and a resort-style pool with 2 waterslides and a swim-up bar.

It is under contract after being listed for $3,785,000

Goodnight! 😍 This stone & brick home is located at 9412 Mafi Court in Great Falls, Virginia  and is situated on 2 acres of land.

It was built in 2020 and features approximately 17,200 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 11 bathrooms, 2-story foyer with floating staircase, elevator, formal living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, family room, wet bar, rec room, wine cellar, home theater, gym, sauna, 4-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, balconies, patios, fireplace, fire pit and an infinity pool with spa.

It sold for $7,000,000 on 02/03/21
